@narfbg have you any update on this patch? For me it works with the additions of the mentioned parts from the notes. New values should be appended to the cached values, e.g. any new where-clause parts should come after any cached parts.

```
$this->$qb_variable = 
    array_merge(
        $this->$qb_cache_var,
        array_udiff(
            $this->$qb_variable,
